query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 s) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ajax',
'transistors')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('dba',
'drupal',
'electronics',
'pt')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Announcer',
'Benefactor',
'Caucus',
'Cleanup',
'Constituent',
'Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Good Question',
'Necromancer',
'Promoter',
'Quorum',
'Self-Learner')
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
